_properties.descriptionZh: 通常指汽车后备箱的容积
_properties.rdfs:comment:
The available volume for cargo or luggage. For automobiles, this is usually the trunk volume.

Typical unit code(s): LTR for liters, FTQ for cubic foot/feet

Note: You can use minValue and maxValue to indicate ranges.
_properties.rdfs:label: cargoVolume

_properties.descriptionZh: 车辆首次在有关公共当局登记的日期。
_properties.rdfs:comment: The date of the first registration of the vehicle with the respective public authorities.
_properties.rdfs:label: dateVehicleFirstRegistered

_properties.descriptionZh: 驱动轮构造，即哪个风轮将经由动力传动系统从车辆的发动机接收扭矩。
_properties.rdfs:comment: The drive wheel configuration, i.e. which roadwheels will receive torque from the vehicle's engine via the drivetrain.
_properties.rdfs:label: driveWheelConfiguration

_properties.descriptionZh: 车辆行驶特定距离或时间所消耗的燃料量（例如每100公里升）
_properties.rdfs:comment:
The amount of fuel consumed for traveling a particular distance or temporal duration with the given vehicle (e.g. liters per 100 km).


Note 1: There are unfortunately no standard unit codes for liters per 100 km.  Use unitText to indicate the unit of measurement, e.g. L/100 km.
Note 2: There are two ways of indicating the fuel consumption, fuelConsumption (e.g. 8 liters per 100 km) and fuelEfficiency (e.g. 30 miles per gallon). They are reciprocal.
Note 3: Often, the absolute value is useful only when related to driving speed ("at 80 km/h") or usage pattern ("city traffic"). You can use valueReference to link the value for the fuel consumption to another value.
_properties.rdfs:label: fuelConsumption

_properties.descriptionZh: 每单位燃料行驶的距离
_properties.rdfs:comment:
The distance traveled per unit of fuel used; most commonly miles per gallon (mpg) or kilometers per liter (km/L).


Note 1: There are unfortunately no standard unit codes for miles per gallon or kilometers per liter. Use unitText to indicate the unit of measurement, e.g. mpg or km/L.
Note 2: There are two ways of indicating the fuel consumption, fuelConsumption (e.g. 8 liters per 100 km) and fuelEfficiency (e.g. 30 miles per gallon). They are reciprocal.
Note 3: Often, the absolute value is useful only when related to driving speed ("at 80 km/h") or usage pattern ("city traffic"). You can use valueReference to link the value for the fuel economy to another value.
_properties.rdfs:label: fuelEfficiency

_properties.descriptionZh: 适用于发动机或发动机的燃料类型。 如果车辆只有一个发动机，该属性可以直接连接到车辆。
_properties.rdfs:comment: The type of fuel suitable for the engine or engines of the vehicle. If the vehicle has only one engine, this property can be attached directly to the vehicle.
_properties.rdfs:label: fuelType

_properties.descriptionZh: 已知汽车故障的文本描述，包括可修复的和不可修复的
_properties.rdfs:comment: A textual description of known damages, both repaired and unrepaired.
_properties.rdfs:label: knownVehicleDamages

_properties.descriptionZh: 由其里程表读取获得的一辆汽车自出厂以来所行驶的总里程
_properties.rdfs:comment:
The total distance travelled by the particular vehicle since its initial production, as read from its odometer.

Typical unit code(s): KMT for kilometers, SMI for statute miles
_properties.rdfs:label: mileageFromOdometer

_properties.descriptionZh: 车辆的安全气囊数
_properties.rdfs:comment: The number or type of airbags in the vehicle.
_properties.rdfs:label: numberOfAirbags

_properties.descriptionZh: 车辆的轴数
_properties.rdfs:comment:
The number of axles.

Typical unit code(s): C62
_properties.rdfs:label: numberOfAxles

_properties.descriptionZh: 车辆的车门数
_properties.rdfs:comment:
The number of doors.

Typical unit code(s): C62
_properties.rdfs:label: numberOfDoors

_properties.descriptionZh: 可用于汽车传动系统的前进档的总数
_properties.rdfs:comment:
The total number of forward gears available for the transmission system of the vehicle.

Typical unit code(s): C62
_properties.rdfs:label: numberOfForwardGears

_properties.descriptionZh: 这辆车的车主数量，包括现在的车主
_properties.rdfs:comment:
The number of owners of the vehicle, including the current one.

Typical unit code(s): C62
_properties.rdfs:label: numberOfPreviousOwners

_properties.descriptionZh: 项目（例：汽车）的生产日期
_properties.rdfs:comment: The date of production of the item, e.g. vehicle.
_properties.rdfs:label: productionDate

_properties.descriptionZh: 物品（例：汽车）被当前物主的购买日期
_properties.rdfs:comment: The date the item e.g. vehicle was purchased by the current owner.
_properties.rdfs:label: purchaseDate

_properties.descriptionZh: 方向盘，或者其他类似设备（主要是汽车的设备）的位置。
_properties.rdfs:comment: The position of the steering wheel or similar device (mostly for cars).
_properties.rdfs:label: steeringPosition

_properties.descriptionZh: 指示车辆配置的简短文本，例如。 '5dr两厢车ST 2.5 MT 225马力'或'限量版'
_properties.rdfs:comment: A short text indicating the configuration of the vehicle, e.g. '5dr hatchback ST 2.5 MT 225 hp' or 'limited edition'.
_properties.rdfs:label: vehicleConfiguration

_properties.descriptionZh: 此车辆发动机的信息
_properties.rdfs:comment: Information about the engine or engines of the vehicle.
_properties.rdfs:label: vehicleEngine

_properties.descriptionZh: 车辆识别号（VIN）是汽车行业用于识别单个机动车辆的唯一序列号
_properties.rdfs:comment: The Vehicle Identification Number (VIN) is a unique serial number used by the automotive industry to identify individual motor vehicles.
_properties.rdfs:label: vehicleIdentificationNumber

_properties.descriptionZh: 车辆内部的颜色或颜色组合
_properties.rdfs:comment: The color or color combination of the interior of the vehicle.
_properties.rdfs:label: vehicleInteriorColor

_properties.descriptionZh: 车辆内部装饰类型或材料（例如合成织物，皮革，木材等）。 虽然大多数车内饰的特点使用材料来表示，但是也可以基于车辆使用或目标受众来表示
_properties.rdfs:comment: The type or material of the interior of the vehicle (e.g. synthetic fabric, leather, wood, etc.). While most interior types are characterized by the material used, an interior type can also be based on vehicle usage or target audience.
_properties.rdfs:label: vehicleInteriorType

_properties.descriptionZh: 车辆型号的发布日期（通常用于将相同版本和型号的车辆做区分）
_properties.rdfs:comment: The release date of a vehicle model (often used to differentiate versions of the same make and model).
_properties.rdfs:label: vehicleModelDate

_properties.descriptionZh: 从实际的物理空间和法律规定的限制两方面的因素，可以容纳的的最多乘客人数。
_properties.rdfs:comment:
The number of passengers that can be seated in the vehicle, both in terms of the physical space available, and in terms of limitations set by law.

Typical unit code(s): C62 for persons.
_properties.rdfs:label: vehicleSeatingCapacity

_properties.descriptionZh: 指示车辆是否用于特殊用途，如商业租赁，驾驶学校或出租车。 许多国家的立法要求在出售汽车时披露这些资料。
_properties.rdfs:comment: Indicates whether the vehicle has been used for special purposes, like commercial rental, driving school, or as a taxi. The legislation in many countries requires this information to be revealed when offering a car for sale.
_properties.rdfs:label: vehicleSpecialUsage

_properties.descriptionZh: 用于将动力从旋转动力源传递到车轮或其他相关部件（“汽车的变速箱”）的组件类型
_properties.rdfs:comment: The type of component used for transmitting the power from a rotating power source to the wheels or other relevant component(s) ("gearbox" for cars).
_properties.rdfs:label: vehicleTransmission

_pTree.descriptionZh: 是指使用于人或货物运输的设备
_pTree.rdfs:comment: A vehicle is a device that is designed or used to transport people or cargo over land, water, air, or through space.
_pTree.rdfs:label: Vehicle

_properties.descriptionZh: 表示实体附加特征的属性值对（例如cnschema.org中没有匹配属性的产品功能或其他特性）
_properties.rdfs:comment:
A property-value pair representing an additional characteristics of the entitity, e.g. a product feature or another characteristic for which there is no matching property in cnschema.org.

Note: Publishers should be aware that applications designed to use specific cnschema.org properties (e.g. http://cnschema.org/width, http://cnschema.org/color, http://cnschema.org/gtin13, ...) will typically expect such data to be provided using those properties, rather than using the generic property/value mechanism.
_properties.rdfs:label: additionalProperty

_properties.descriptionZh: 12位全球贸易品项识别码
_properties.rdfs:comment: The GTIN-12 code of the product, or the product to which the offer refers. The GTIN-12 is the 12-digit GS1 Identification Key composed of a U.P.C. Company Prefix, Item Reference, and Check Digit used to identify trade items. See GS1 GTIN Summary for more details.
_properties.rdfs:label: gtin12

_properties.descriptionZh: 13位全球贸易品项识别码
_properties.rdfs:comment: The GTIN-13 code of the product, or the product to which the offer refers. This is equivalent to 13-digit ISBN codes and EAN UCC-13. Former 12-digit UPC codes can be converted into a GTIN-13 code by simply adding a preceeding zero. See GS1 GTIN Summary for more details.
_properties.rdfs:label: gtin13

_properties.descriptionZh: 14位全球贸易品项识别码
_properties.rdfs:comment: The GTIN-14 code of the product, or the product to which the offer refers. See GS1 GTIN Summary for more details.
_properties.rdfs:label: gtin14

_properties.descriptionZh: 8位全球贸易品项识别码
_properties.rdfs:comment: The GTIN-8 code of the product, or the product to which the offer refers. This code is also known as EAN/UCC-8 or 8-digit EAN. See GS1 GTIN Summary for more details.
_properties.rdfs:label: gtin8

_properties.descriptionZh: 高度
_properties.rdfs:comment: The height of the item.

_properties.descriptionZh: 指明此产品是消耗品的另一产品（或多个产品）的指针。

_properties.descriptionZh: 跟它相关

_properties.descriptionZh: 跟它相似

_properties.rdfs:comment: A predefined value from OfferItemCondition or a textual description of the condition of the product or service, or the products or services included in the offer.

_properties.descriptionZh: 该项的一个附加类型， 通常用于从外部词典中向微数据语法添加更加具体的类型。它表示事物和事物本身所属的类之间的关系。在RDFa语法中, 对多类型最好使用‘typeof’属性这样的本地RDFa语法. Schema.org 工具对额外类型的理解较弱，特别是外部定义的额外类型。
_properties.rdfs:comment: An additional type for the item, typically used for adding more specific types from external vocabularies in microdata syntax. This is a relationship between something and a class that the thing is in. In RDFa syntax, it is better to use the native RDFa syntax - the 'typeof' attribute - for multiple types. Schema.org tools may have only weaker understanding of extra types, in particular those defined externally.
_properties.rdfs:label: additionalType
